{"tid":490484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發🌹🌹】Cash死左！！！！？！","createTime":"2017-12-05T16:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T04:20:11.000Z","uid":5812,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"142907425ae6b590a71d620a23422787bb8362f2","tid":490484,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"【Cash一路好走 🌹🌹】鄺美雲的愛犬Cash於兩星期前，被檢測出左邊腎及胰臟生了腫瘤，癌細胞更擴散至淋巴，需要被送進動物醫院的深切治療部進行急救。平日精靈的Cash呼吸變得氣若游絲，連進食都有困難。飽受病痛折磨的Cash努力抗癌，希望能有日回家與主人團聚。<br />\n<br />\n可惜延至星期日凌晨時分，14歲半的Cash終於不敵癌魔，離開了深愛牠的主人。雖然明白生死有命，但Cash的離去仍為鄺美雲帶來無限傷感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/165522_d92034b847d693aac6c5ae18cf417e20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F165522_d92034b847d693aac6c5ae18cf417e20.jpg&h=c5298872&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea721c9100a09318d6502f4bc510da0ee385e2b7","tid":490484,"uid":103380,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"衰撚過馬英九睇錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e635152745f5c004d52e63e1b35ab63de16a17","tid":490484,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8734e9dd4ec5568354052e8b849126e93eb176b0","tid":490484,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440523650d826303423f7509cb3c816cfb4e97fc","tid":490484,"uid":17368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"Money已經夠衰，到底要幾愛錢先會叫隻狗做Cash"},{"pid":"9b371011ab1450e5cf31d88d62f9565a78d5ceaa","tid":490484,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T22:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0709347efc904e13938225dff07a4f80ab5951","tid":490484,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/14202053/image1510662017027.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F14202053%2Fimage1510662017027.png&h=8afa3890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">鄺美雲近年亦與香港政壇關係密切，並不時發表政治表態言論。</span>去年9月舉行立法會選舉前，她除表明支持新東候選人工聯會鄧家彪連任外，更為同區出選的新民黨容海恩拍宣傳片，大讚對方友善，可為香港帶來正能量。同年12月的特首選委選舉，<span style=\"color: violet;\">她亦與汪明荃及導演高志森組成「文化共融」參選。</span>近期《國歌法》引起各界爭議，<span style=\"color: red;\">她就強調港人對於身為中國人要感恩，又指「你照吓鏡，你是中國人」，她亦認為不尊重國歌的人反叛，覺得這樣做有型、與眾不同。</span>"},{"pid":"b0d5335e114c9fc0c04e634273bdefbff75976f1","tid":490484,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171201/s00001/ab6e1d83aa22118923d8011206a116a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171201%2Fs00001%2Fab6e1d83aa22118923d8011206a116a3.jpg&h=dbad6120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【港區人代選舉】鄺美雲挾380提名參選　包括范太汪明荃"},{"pid":"7f0d2bd0d7e03434cc8465b2fb1de8329e40923e","tid":490484,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩大淫婦臭雞</span></span><br />\n「汪阿姐2.0」？　傳鄺美雲參選人大獲「祝福」　曾撐國歌法<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/132565/thumbnail/cb3f76abab54a99b138fa285a31c3a8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F132565%2Fthumbnail%2Fcb3f76abab54a99b138fa285a31c3a8d.jpg&h=5de8ebe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲VS汪阿姐<br />\n<br />\n年齡<br />\n鄺美雲：54歲　汪明荃：70歲<br />\n<br />\n出身<br />\n鄺美雲：1982年香港小姐亞軍　汪明荃：1967年加入麗的映聲1971年轉投無綫電視<br />\n<br />\n主要政績<br />\n鄺美雲：現任江西省政協委員、中華海外聯誼會理事及香港珠海社團總會會長。<br />\n汪明荃：曾任香港八和會館理事會主席及港區人大代表，至今擔任全國政協委員二十年。<br />\n<br />\n感情生活<br />\n鄺美雲：<br />\n1996年與演員呂良偉結婚，一年後離婚。<br />\n1983年與<span style=\"color: red;\">鄭裕彤兒子鄭家成拍拖，1986年分手。<br />\n為鄭裕彤紅顏知己，相交三十年。</span><br />\n2001年曾被媒體稱為何鴻燊的「五姨太」，後來與賭王正式上契，成為其契女。<br />\n被指曾與前亞姐曹央雲、嘉域集團（186）幕後話事人何永安鬧出三角緋聞；前者成功跑出，為男方誕下三女。<br />\n2012年與恒基兆業地產營業部總經理林達民相戀，三年後分手。<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃 (四家姓奴)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ErvTTDh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FErvTTDh.jpg&h=b62afa5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lAjzlru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlAjzlru.jpg&h=73e2a7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1971年與毛織廠老闆劉昌華結婚，曾經歷一次小產，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kRH42fh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkRH42fh.jpg&h=de9931c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與何守信因合作《歡樂今宵》而傳緋聞，二人最終因性格不合分開。<br />\n(汪氏婚後同已婚何b 偷情)<br />\n<br />\n1982年離婚。<br />\n<br />\n1988年起與羅家英交往，男方多次公開求婚均被拒，直至2009年結婚。"},{"pid":"ab47ac729057d04821ddf9c1a373515faa01c86a","tid":490484,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}